Question 1: What is the name of the hidden "history" file in the htb-user's home directory?
Solution 1: ls -a (yields all directories and files within the current directory, including hidden ones)

Question 2: What is the index number of the "sudoers" file in the "/etc" directory?
Solution 2: "ls -i /etc/sudoers" (This prints just the index number for whatever file you select, in this case, "sudoers"
